methods.getStaticSymbolTable:
Get a static Table view of this SymbolTableSource's symbol table, providing a many:1 or 1:1 mapping of
 unique long identifiers to the symbol values in this source.

:param sourceIndex: (io.deephaven.engine.rowset.RowSet) - The RowSet whose keys must be mappable via the result Table's identifier
        column
:param useLookupCaching: (boolean) - Hint whether symbol lookups performed to generate the symbol table should apply caching.
        Implementations may ignore this hint.
:return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.Table) The symbol table
methods.getSymbolTable:
Get a Table view of this SymbolTableSource's symbol table, providing a many:1 or 1:1 mapping of unique
 long identifiers to the symbol values in this source.

 
 The result will be refreshing if table is refreshing.

:param sourceTable: (io.deephaven.engine.table.impl.QueryTable) - The QueryTable whose row keys must be mappable via the result Table's
        identifier column
:param useLookupCaching: (boolean) - Hint whether symbol lookups performed to generate the symbol table should apply caching.
        Implementations may ignore this hint.
:return: (io.deephaven.engine.table.Table) The symbol table
methods.hasSymbolTable:
:param sourceIndex: (io.deephaven.engine.rowset.RowSet) - The RowSet whose keys must be mappable
:return: (boolean) Whether this SymbolTableSource can provide a symbol table that covers all keys in sourceIndex.

text:
Interface for ColumnSources that can provide a Table view of their symbol tables, providing a many:1
 or 1:1 mapping of unique long identifiers to the symbol values in this source.
 
 Such sources are also expected to be reinterpretable (ColumnSource.allowsReinterpret(Class)) as long
ColumnSources of the same identifiers.
